                        <interp inst="t18431023-name-307" type="given" value="WILLIAM"></interp>WILLIAM POCOCK</persName>
                  </hi> (<hi rend="italic">police-constable F</hi> 81.) I assisted in stopping the pri<lb></lb>soner, and found the lead on him.</p>
               <p>(The prisoner received a good character.)</p>
